'''Unmilled Rice''' is a [[Vegetables|vegetable]] [[Crops|crop]] that grows from [[Rice Shoot]]s  after 8 days (6 when irrigated). Unmilled Rice is harvested using a [[Scythe]].

Players have the ability to craft [[Rice]] from Unmilled Rice by using a [[Mill]]. Once placed in the Mill, one Unmilled Rice will make one [[Rice]]. Rice will appear in the box on the right side of the Mill the following morning.

==Stages==
When harvested, each Rice Shoot gives one Unmilled Rice, with a 10% chance of one or more extra rice (0.11 more rice on average).<ref name="extra_rice">The game generates a random number between 0 and 1, and if it is less than 0.1, then another Unmilled Rice will spawn. This repeats until the random number is greater than or equal to 0.1, at which point the chance for an extra Unmilled Rice ends. This, on average, will give 0.11 extra Unmilled Rice. Keep in mind that [[Luck]] can also double the amount of extra Unmilled Rice spawned by the above formula.</ref>

