==Tailoring==
Unmilled Rice can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring|Shirt And Belt]].  [[File:Shirt159.png|24px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as an orange dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
*Unmilled Rice may be randomly requested in [[Spring]] at the [[Quests#Help Wanted Quests|"Help Wanted" board]] outside [[Pierre's General Store]] for a reward of {{Price|90}} and 150 [[Friendship]] points.

==Notes==
*If grown from [[Rice Shoot]]s purchased from [[Pierre's General Store|Pierre's]], it is only profitable to sell gold quality Unmilled Rice directly. With the [[Skills#Farming|Tiller Profession]], silver quality Unmilled Rice becomes profitable by {{price|1}}.  In all cases it is profitable to process Unmilled Rice into [[Rice]] using a [[Mill]], or [[Jellies and Pickles|Pickles]] using a [[Preserves Jar]].
*The day you harvest an Unmilled Rice from an irrigated tile, the tile retains the irrigation water. Anything you plant there that same day will not need watering.

